articles.description: Just hours after beloved Jeopardy! host Alex Trebek passed away, his Wheel of Fortune colleagues Pat Sajak and Vanna White penned touching tributes.
articles.content: Just hours after beloved Jeopardy! host Alex Trebek passed away following his lengthy battle with pancreatic cancer, his Wheel of Fortune colleagues Pat Sajak and Vanna White penned touching tributes… [+2766 chars]
